{
  "uid": "observability-tracing",
  "title": "70-Observability — Tracing",
  "tags": ["homelab", "observability", "tracing"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "editable": false,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "refresh": "1m",
  "time": { "from": "now-6h", "to": "now" },
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "service",
        "type": "query",
        "label": "Service",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
        "query": { "qryType": 1, "query": "label_values(traces_spanmetrics_calls_total{source=\"tempo\"}, service)" },
        "refresh": 2,
        "includeAll": true,
        "multi": false,
        "current": { "text": "All", "value": "$__all" }
      }
    ]
  },
  "links": [
    { "title": "Home", "type": "link", "icon": "home", "url": "/d/home-server-health", "tooltip": "00-Home — Server health", "targetBlank": false, "keepTime": true, "includeVars": false }
  ],
  "annotations": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "Deploys",
        "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
        "enable": true,
        "iconColor": "rgba(0, 211, 255, 1)",
        "expr": "{compose_service=\"doco-cd\"} |~ \"(?i)deploy.*success\"",
        "target": { "expr": "{compose_service=\"doco-cd\"} |~ \"(?i)deploy.*success\"", "refId": "Anno" }
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 700,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "RED — per service",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "w": 24, "h": 1 }
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Request rate per service",
      "description": "Rate of spans (kind=server/consumer) per service, derived from Tempo's metrics-generator span_metrics processor. Variable `$service` narrows the view.",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 1, "w": 12, "h": 7 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (service) (rate(traces_spanmetrics_calls_total{source=\"tempo\", service=~\"$service\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{service}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "lineWidth": 1, "fillOpacity": 10, "showPoints": "never" }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "right", "showLegend": true, "calcs": ["mean", "max"] }, "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" } }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Error rate per service",
      "description": "Share of spans with status_code=STATUS_CODE_ERROR per service.",
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 1, "w": 12, "h": 7 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (service) (rate(traces_spanmetrics_calls_total{source=\"tempo\", service=~\"$service\", status_code=\"STATUS_CODE_ERROR\"}[$__rate_interval])) / clamp_min(sum by (service) (rate(traces_spanmetrics_calls_total{source=\"tempo\", service=~\"$service\"}[$__rate_interval])), 0.001)",
          "legendFormat": "{{service}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 1,
          "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "lineWidth": 1, "fillOpacity": 10, "showPoints": "never" },
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [{ "color": "green", "value": null }, { "color": "orange", "value": 0.01 }, { "color": "red", "value": 0.05 }] }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "right", "showLegend": true, "calcs": ["mean", "max"] }, "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" } }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Latency p95 per service",
      "description": "p95 of span duration per service. Spikes here are the entry point for 'why is X slow?' — click a point and use Explore → Tempo to find the slow trace.",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 8, "w": 24, "h": 7 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le, service) (rate(traces_spanmetrics_latency_bucket{source=\"tempo\", service=~\"$service\"}[$__rate_interval])))",
          "legendFormat": "{{service}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "lineWidth": 1, "fillOpacity": 0, "showPoints": "never" }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "right", "showLegend": true, "calcs": ["mean", "max"] }, "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" } }
    },
    {
      "id": 701,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Service graph",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 15, "w": 24, "h": 1 }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Edge request rate (client → server)",
      "description": "Number of requests per minute between each pair of services, computed by Tempo's service_graphs processor from matched client/server spans.",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 16, "w": 12, "h": 8 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (client, server) (rate(traces_service_graph_request_total{source=\"tempo\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{client}} → {{server}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "lineWidth": 1, "fillOpacity": 10, "showPoints": "never" }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "right", "showLegend": true, "calcs": ["mean", "max"] }, "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" } }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Edge failure rate (client → server)",
      "description": "Failed-request share per edge. Useful for spotting one upstream silently degrading the rest of the graph.",
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 16, "w": 12, "h": 8 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (client, server) (rate(traces_service_graph_request_failed_total{source=\"tempo\"}[$__rate_interval])) / clamp_min(sum by (client, server) (rate(traces_service_graph_request_total{source=\"tempo\"}[$__rate_interval])), 0.001)",
          "legendFormat": "{{client}} → {{server}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 1,
          "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "lineWidth": 1, "fillOpacity": 10, "showPoints": "never" },
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [{ "color": "green", "value": null }, { "color": "orange", "value": 0.01 }, { "color": "red", "value": 0.05 }] }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "right", "showLegend": true, "calcs": ["mean", "max"] }, "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" } }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "type": "nodeGraph",
      "title": "Service graph (live)",
      "description": "Live service map rendered from Tempo's service_graphs metrics. Click a node to drill into trace search filtered to that service.",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 24, "w": 24, "h": 10 },
      "datasource": { "type": "tempo", "uid": "tempo" },
      "targets": [
        { "refId": "A", "queryType": "serviceMap", "datasource": { "type": "tempo", "uid": "tempo" } }
      ],
      "options": {}
    },
    {
      "id": 702,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Top callers",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 34, "w": 24, "h": 1 }
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "type": "bargauge",
      "title": "Top 10 spans by call rate",
      "description": "Highest-rate (service, span name) pairs over the dashboard time range. Useful for 'where is the volume going?' questions.",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 35, "w": 12, "h": 8 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "topk(10, sum by (service, span_name) (rate(traces_spanmetrics_calls_total{source=\"tempo\"}[$__range])))",
          "legendFormat": "{{service}} / {{span_name}}",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "unit": "reqps", "color": { "mode": "continuous-BlPu" } },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "displayMode": "gradient", "orientation": "horizontal", "showUnfilled": true }
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "type": "bargauge",
      "title": "Top 10 spans by p95 latency",
      "description": "Slowest (service, span name) pairs at p95. Hover-then-Explore on a bar to open the corresponding traces in Tempo.",
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 35, "w": 12, "h": 8 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "topk(10, histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le, service, span_name) (rate(traces_spanmetrics_latency_bucket{source=\"tempo\"}[$__range]))))",
          "legendFormat": "{{service}} / {{span_name}}",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "unit": "s", "color": { "mode": "continuous-YlOrRd" } },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "displayMode": "gradient", "orientation": "horizontal", "showUnfilled": true }
    },
    {
      "id": 703,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Open in Explore",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 43, "w": 24, "h": 1 }
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Trace search",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 44, "w": 24, "h": 4 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "Tempo replaces the Jaeger UI — use **Grafana → Explore → Tempo** for trace search.\n\n- [Open Tempo Explore](/explore?left=%7B%22datasource%22:%22tempo%22,%22queries%22:%5B%7B%22queryType%22:%22traceqlSearch%22%7D%5D%7D) — empty TraceQL search across all services.\n- Useful TraceQL starters:\n  - `{ resource.service.name=\"reverse-proxy\" && duration > 1s }` — slow Traefik requests.\n  - `{ status = error }` — every failing span in range.\n  - `{ span.http.status_code >= 500 }` — server errors only.\n- Each time-series panel above supports right-click → *View in Explore* with the panel's time range pre-applied."
      }
    }
  ]
}
